column1: #Text=The Sacramento Kings ( 16 - 25 ) defeated the Sacramento Kings ( 16 - 25 ) 98 - 94 on Wednesday at the Moda Center in Portland .
#Text=The Kings got off to a quick start in this one , out - scoring the Kings 31 - 23 right away in the first quarter .

#Text=The Kings were the superior shooters in this game , going 45 percent from the field and 33 percent from the three - point line , while the Kings went just 40 percent from the floor and just 31 percent from deep .
#Text=The Trail Blazers were also able to force the Kings into 21 turnovers , while committing only 13 of their own .
#Text=The Trail Blazers 000 next game will be at home against the Los Angeles Clippers on Wednesday , while the Blazers will be at home against the Los Angeles Clippers on Wednesday .
